                      <td align="left" style="padding-top: 20px; font-family: 'Open Sans', Verdana, sans-serif; color: #666666; font-size: 16px;" class="padding-copy iphone-text iphone-fix"><font face="'Open Sans', Verdana, sans-serif">Use tools to help you, such as Gantt charts or Kanban boards. The visual displays make it easy to quickly decide on important tasks and follow them through to completion.</font></td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td class="padding-copy">
                  <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="padding-top:20px; text-align: center;">
